column5: Its been pretty slow down here on the shouth shore of ontario around the pier heads so far. Thats been a theme for quite some time now actually. Of course , timing is everything.........but hitting that right time has become more difficult over the past few years for sure.  I still plug away as i enjoy just taking a ride and launching some hardware around the estuaries..........
I feel better knowing I was not the only one that had a tough season
Pulaskie N.Y- Fish caught in lake Ontario can now be safely eaten on a more regular basis~~ up to four meals a month.

and that is why they are at the ganny now taking eggs of wild fish  to see if they can get the salmon that stage early will help the boats out in lake ontario .. it will be a two year project to start
